DataElement.preferredDefinition: A single human being.:Pertaining to biology or to life and living things.:An independently existing thing (living or nonliving)._The event of being born.:An expression of both date and time that an event has happened or will happen._The year of birth of the person. For data sources with date of birth, the year is extracted. For data sources where the year of birth is not available, the approximate year of birth is derived based on any age group categorization available.
